override.description:
Delimit the modifications for material part attributes.
Examples: | # | # Select the parent part | # | ensight.part.select_begin(1) | # | ensight.material.begin() | # | # create a domain type material part | # | ensight.material.type("domain") | ensight.material.subdivide("2") | # | # use the two materials shown | # | ensight.material.select_byname_begin("matl_02","matl_03") | ensight.material.end() | ensight.material.create()
Returns: zero on success, non-zero on error

Create a material part with the currently defined attributes using the currently selected parts as parent parts.
Examples: | # | # Select the parent part | # | ensight.part.select_begin(1) | # | ensight.material.begin() | # | # create a domain type material part | # | ensight.material.type("domain") | ensight.material.subdivide("2") | # | # use the two materials shown | # | ensight.material.select_byname_begin("matl_02","matl_03") | ensight.material.end() | ensight.material.create()
Returns: zero on success, non-zero on error

Sets the target to the default settings for subsequent attribute modifications.
Examples: | ensight.material.select_default() | ensight.part.modify_begin() | ensight.material.type("domain") | ensight.part.modify_end()
Returns: zero on success, non-zero on error

Set the accuracy of the resulting material part - higher values result in higher fidelity.
Args: p0: 'level'
* 1 * 2 * 3
Examples: | # | # Select the parent part | # | ensight.part.select_begin(1) | # | ensight.material.begin() | # | # create a domain type material part | # | ensight.material.type("domain") | ensight.material.subdivide("2") | # | # use the two materials shown | # | ensight.material.select_byname_begin("matl_02","matl_03") | ensight.material.end() | ensight.material.create()
Returns: zero on success, non-zero on error

Set the resulting material part to be a domain or interface through/between the material selected.
Args: p0: 'type'
* domain * interface
Examples: | # | # Select the parent part | # | ensight.part.select_begin(1) | # | ensight.material.begin() | # | # create a domain type material part | # | ensight.material.type("domain") | ensight.material.subdivide("2") | # | # use the two materials shown | # | ensight.material.select_byname_begin("matl_02","matl_03") | ensight.material.end() | ensight.material.create()
Returns: zero on success, non-zero on error
